
Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which this addon collects and uses information collected from users (each, a "User").

No personal identification information is collected from users.

Non-personal identification information: the only information collected is the hostname of visited website send to server for checking/updating website rating data.

How is collected information used: it's only used for maintaining the database of rating of any website.

How is information collected: HTTPS is used.

Changes to this privacy policy: The author has the discretion to update this privacy policy at any time. When it's updated, it will be included in any distribution published by the author to replace previous privacy policy.

Your acceptance of these terms:

By using this Application, you signify your acceptance of this policy. If you do not agree to this policy, please do not use the application. Your continued use of the Application following the posting of changes to this policy will be deemed your acceptance of those changes. 
